Division By Zero
----------------


<div class="fragment">
\begin{spec}
λ> let average xs = sum xs `div` length xs

λ> average [100, 202, 300]
2
\end{spec}
</div>

<br>

<div class="fragment">
\begin{spec}
λ> average []
*** Exception: divide by zero
\end{spec}


